title.rendered: Alticor Inc Donates 3000+ Pounds of Food

content.rendered: Alticor Inc donated 3,701 pounds of food for the Second Harvest Food Bank’s Stand Up for Kids Food Drive. To turn up the heat on the food drive, Alticor Inc made it a competition between job site offices and challenged them to donate as many barrels of food as possible. At the end of this friendly competition, Alticor Inc’ Northern California District filled over 17 barrels of food.
